llowing day with no online renewals stanford faculty and staff 3 days due at closing on the third day with 1 online renewal for each item stanford temporary staff visiting scholars faculty spouses continuing studies students and continuing studies lecturers 3 days due at closing the following day with no online renewals reserves 2 hours journals bound and current locked stack items microforms and stanford dissertations and theses do not circulate books are subject to recall after one week if requested by another user renewal of loans is permitted if no holds or recalls have been placed on those items for circulation information regarding the vrc slide collection please see the vrc page for more circulation assistance call 650 723 3408 or send an email to artlibrary stanford edu art architecture and design group menu back stanford university stanford california 94305 650 725 1064 terms of use copyright complaints
